---

// // G-B Campaign Website - Major (Retd.) Fahad Hanif Khan
// Class & Integrity Tier: Midnight Sapphire & Antique Champagne Gold
import '../styles/global.css';

---

<html lang="ur">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Major (Retd.) Fahad Hanif Khan | Astore Halqa-1</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-[#080D18] text-slate-200 font-english antialiased selection:bg-[#C5A25D] selection:text-[#080D18] overflow-x-hidden">

    <header class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-[#080D18]/80 backdrop-blur-3xl border-b border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-5 flex justify-between items-center">
        
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#D4B26F] to-[#A37F3D] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(197,162,93,0.15)]">
            <span class="text-white text-base">🎖️</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-widest text-white uppercase leading-none">Astore <span class="text-[#C5A25D]">Halqa-1</span></h1>
            <p class="text-[9px] text-[#C5A25D] tracking-[0.3em] font-semibold uppercase mt-1">Campaign Secretariat 2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <nav class="hidden lg:flex space-x-12 font-semibold text-[11px] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-slate-400">
          <a href="#about" class="hover:text-[#C5A25D] transition-colors duration-300">The Major</a>
          <a href="#anthem" class="hover:text-[#C5A25D] transition-colors duration-300">Campaign Anthem</a>
          <a href="#mission" class="hover:text-[#C5A25D] transition-colors duration-300">The Blueprint</a>
        </nav>

        <a href="https://wa.me/923000000000?text=Assalam-o-Alaikum%20Major%20Fahad,%20I%20wish%20to%20support%20your%20campaign" 
           class="border border-[#C5A25D] text-[#C5A25D] hover:bg-[#C5A25D] hover:text-[#080D18] px-7 py-2.5 rounded-full font-bold text-xs tracking-widest transition-all duration-300">
          JOIN COALITION
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      
      <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-28 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 bg-[radial-gradient(#C5A25D_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:32px_32px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#C5A25D]/5 rounded-full blur-[180px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-blue-900/10 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 w-full relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-3 border-l-2 border-[#C5A25D] pl-4 py-1">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#C5A25D] uppercase">A Legacy of Honor & Duty</span>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light tracking-tight leading-[1.05] text-white">
              Major (Retd.) <br/>
              <span class="font-black tracking-tighter uppercase text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-[#EAD09D] to-white">Fahad Hanif</span><br/>
              <span class="font-black tracking-tighter uppercase">Khan</span>
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-4" dir="rtl">
              <p class="font-urdu text-4xl text-white font-bold leading-relaxed text-right">
                استور کی بقا، ترقی اور دیانتدار قیادت کا ضامن
              </p>
              <p class="font-urdu text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-xl text-right">
                عسکری نظم و ضبط، تعلیمی شعور اور حلقہ ۱ کی تعمیرِ نو۔ ہم کھوکھلے وعدوں پر نہیں، صرف ٹھوس اور میرٹ پر مبنی فیصلوں پر یقین رکھتے ہیں۔
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4">
              <a href="https://wa.me/923000000000" 
                 class="bg-[#C5A25D] hover:bg-[#EAD09D] text-[#080D18] text-center font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(197,162,93,0.15)]">
                Connect Directly
              </a>
              <a href="#anthem" class="border border-white/10 hover:border-[#C5A25D] text-slate-300 hover:text-white text-center font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
                Listen to Campaign Anthem
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            
            <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-gradient-to-b from-[#111A2E] to-[#0A101C] border border-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase px-12 text-center">
                 [Official Portrait of Major Fahad Hanif Khan]
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#080D18] via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
              
              <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-[#080D18]/70 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[9px] text-[#C5A25D] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Candidate Portfolio</p>
                  <p class="text-md font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-0.5">Astore Halqa-1 Nominee</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-sm">🏔️</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div id="anthem" class="bg-[#0D1525] border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:border-[#C5A25D]/20 transition-all duration-500">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#C5A25D]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-lg text-[#C5A25D] border border-[#C5A25D]/20">
                  🎙️
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <span class="bg-[#C5A25D]/10 text-[#C5A25D] text-[9px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider">Campaign Music</span>
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-1">Me Major Fahad Hanif Zila Astor Shan Hanu</h4>
                  <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400">Featuring Raees Malik • Traditional Shina</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kHzXvCfKQ0s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                   class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-red-600/10 hover:bg-red-600/20 text-red-400 border border-red-500/10 font-bold text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider py-2.5 px-4 rounded-full transition-all">
                  <span>▶</span> <span>Watch Video on YouTube</span>
                </a>
                <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Astore Folk Release</span>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="mission" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 border-t border-white/5">
        <div class="mb-20 max-w-2xl">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#C5A25D] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">Policy & Direction</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white tracking-tight mt-3">The Blueprint for <span class="font-black italic">Development</span></h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-4 leading-relaxed">Systematic, calculated reforms engineered to lift Astore's local administrative standards and infrastructure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 auto-rows-[220px]">
          
          <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bg-[#0C1322] rounded-3xl p-10 border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-end group hover:border-[#C5A25D]/20 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 text-[180px] opacity-[0.01] pointer-events-none">🏔️</div>
            <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
              <span class="bg-[#C5A25D]/10 text-[#C5A25D] text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Priority One</span>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Fortifying Winter Logistics</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm">Restructuring storage distribution models and mountain pass connectivity guidelines to protect Astore from seasonal supply cuts.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#0C1322] rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-[#C5A25D]/20 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div class="text-2xl text-[#C5A25D]">⚖️</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Meritocratic Governance</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs mt-1 leading-relaxed">Applying uncompromising military precision to local fund distributions and council operations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#C5A25D] to-[#A37F3D] text-[#080D18] rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-2xl">🎓</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black uppercase tracking-tight leading-none">High-Altitude Youth Command</h4>
              <p class="text-[#080D18]/80 text-xs font-semibold mt-2 leading-relaxed">Developing training institutions and tourism infrastructure to convert raw talent into long-term careers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-[#0C1322] border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-8 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Direct Civil Welfare</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Equal, transparent resource sharing across all hamlets of Halqa-1.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="font-urdu text-lg text-[#C5A25D] text-right font-bold ml-4 shrink-0" dir="rtl">
              بلا تفریق اور دیانتدارانہ نمائندگی
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0C1322] to-[#080D18] border-t border-white/5 py-24 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-12">
          <div class="text-right space-y-4" dir="rtl">
            <h2 class="font-urdu text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white font-bold leading-tight">
              استور کے ایک نئے روشن کل کا آغاز کریں
            </h2>
            <p class="font-urdu text-xl text-slate-400">
              مادرِ وطن کے ایک سپاہی کی قیادت پر بھروسہ کریں۔ آئیں مل کر مہم کو آگے بڑھائیں۔
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://wa.me/923000000000?text=I%20want%20to%20volunteer%20for%20Major%20Fahad" 
             class="bg-[#C5A25D] hover:bg-[#EAD09D] text-[#080D18] px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl">
            Volunteer For Halqa-1
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="py-12 border-t border-white/5 bg-[#050911] text-center text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
        <p>© 2026 Secretariat of Major (R) Fahad Hanif Khan</p>
        <div class="border border-white/5 px-4 py-2 rounded text-slate-500 text-[9px]">
          Constructed for Astore Halqa-1
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Nastaliq+Urdu:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;900&display=swap');
  
  .font-urdu { font-family: 'Noto Nastaliq Urdu', serif; }
  .font-english { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
</style>